<p><b>134
</b>  Previous reports on the Special Rapporteur have also discussed the prohibition of mandatory 
</p>
<p>death sentences briefly.  A/61/311, para. 57; E/CN.4/2005/7, paras. 63-64; E/CN.4/2002/74, 
