also constitutes a violation of Article 6.  <i>See </i>ICCPR, art. 6(2):  &#8220;sentence of death may be 
imposed only &#8230; not contrary to the provisions of the present Covenant&#8221;. 
<b>141
</b></p>
<p>  <i>See also</i> E/CN.4/2006/53/Add.1, 232-242. 
